(39, 'alice_beseme@care.org.ge', 'women with disabilities', 'Dear Sir or Madam,\n\nI am writing with regard to the situation of disabled women in Georgia. \n\nI work at the NGO CARE International in the Caucasus and we are about to launch a project towards women with disabilities living in Samtredia, Abasha and Senaki. I would like to get some information about the situation of disabled people (and more specifically women) in Georgia, the problems they face and some more specific issues (employment, education, etc).\n\nI know that you have some knowledge on this topic, since you have built projects directed towards disabled women. Would it be possible to meet, next week or the week after, a member of the Partnership for Human rights who could provide me with some information on the subject?\n \nThank you in advance for your answer.\n\nYours faithfully,\nAlice Beseme\n', 0, '2015-09-04 08:26:06', '2015-09-04 08:26:06'),
(40, 'tako25tako@yahoo.com', 'bavshvis uflebebi', 'Gamarjoba!   me gaxlavart tamar antadze . myavs tyupebi . tyupebi dadian  barnovis quchaze mdebare ,,wignierebis skola  asfurcela,,shi, .. davdivart   3 kviraa,,,, pirvel periodshi vifikre rom axl dawyebuli iyo da  davelode gamosworebas,, maqvs pretenzia kvebastan dakavshirebit.. is rac me manaxes meniushi  aris sul sxva ,, realurad bavshvebi dges movidnen mshivrebi... moxarshuli grechixis mets samxarze ar tavazoben arafers.... dzalian gtxovt ikneb  damexmarot  ,, rom daicvas is pirobebi rasac gvtavazobs,,,  pativiscemit      T . antadze .  ', 0, '2015-10-15 18:49:35', '2015-10-15 18:49:35');
